Subject: Re: [T2] Fuel Injector Replacement

Simply clamp off the lines. You should own a set of
plastic fuel hose clamps anyway for changing fuel
filters. They clamp flexible hose sections so no fuel
can flow.
http://store.summitracing.com/partdetail.asp?autofilter=1&part=SUM%2DW84017&N=700+115&autoview=sku
-BaH
